snippet.title: SUBTERFUGE - surfacing on iOS and Android October 15!
snippet.description:
A game by Ron Carmel and Noel Llopis.
Join our alpha by signing up for our mailing list at http://subterfuge-game.com 
Follow @SubterfugeGame on twitter: http://twitter.com/SubterfugeGame

Our gratitude to everyone who made this trailer happen!

An AREA 5 Production // area5.tv, Cesar Quintero, Ryan O'Donnell, Matt Chandronait, Jason Bertrand
Music by Francisco Cerda // http://cerdamusic.com, @FranciscoFoco
Adam Sessler as Alex
MacKenzie Paulus as Beth
Matt Chandronait as Charlie
Shawne Benson as Diane
David Hellman as Eric
Greg Rice as Frank

Special thanks to Seana Mickolsm, Eleanor Van Slyke, Paul Greenleaf, Steve Lima, Talia Chriqui, Pi Bar, Humble Bundle, and The Stable Cafe.
